{"title":"cf#E49(1027)","date":"2018-08-18T16:00:00.000Z","author":"luoyayu","excerpt":"","slug":"2018-08-19-cf_E49_1027","comments":true,"tags":["codeforces"],"categories":["ACM"],"updated":"2018-08-19T06:47:45.000Z","content":"<h1 id=\"A-签到题\"><a href=\"#A-签到题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"A 签到题\"></a>A 签到题</h1><p>注意字符必须改变，有(ab, xy)肯定是不行的</p>\n<h1 id=\"B-填数-规律\"><a href=\"#B-填数-规律\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"B 填数+规律\"></a>B 填数+规律</h1><h2 id=\"题意\"><a href=\"#题意\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题意\"></a>题意</h2><p>在n<em>n的网格中填数，先1~ceil(n</em>n/2)顺序填(x+y)是偶数的格子，在填(x+y)是奇数的格子<br>例如n=4, n=5的情况<br><img src=\"http://codeforces.com/predownloaded/24/b6/24b647c14fca3cb512e5c35d990ae8cc535ec585.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"做法一：分类讨论\"><a href=\"#做法一：分类讨论\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"做法一：分类讨论\"></a>做法一：分类讨论</h2><p>按(x+y)奇偶，再讨论x,y的奇偶</p>\n<h2 id=\"做法二：规律\"><a href=\"#做法二：规律\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"做法二：规律\"></a>做法二：规律</h2><p>(x+y)是偶数的位置的值全部减去右下角的值会发现其实也是1~ceil(n*n/2)的填数<br>对于这种情况其值为$\\displaystyle n\\frac{x-1}{2}+\\frac{y+1}{2}$</p>\n<h2 id=\"code\"><a href=\"#code\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"code\"></a>code</h2><iframe id=\"iFrame0\" name=\"iFrame0\" width=\"100%\" onload=\"this.height=iFrame0.document.body.scrollHeight\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"/htmlcode/cf/cf1027b.html\" scrolling=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"yes\"></iframe>\n\n<h1 id=\"C-签到题\"><a href=\"#C-签到题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"C 签到题\"></a>C 签到题</h1><p>$nlog(n)+O(n)$ 排序扫一遍, 最小化$\\frac{a}{b}+\\frac{b}{a}$即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"code-1\"><a href=\"#code-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"code\"></a>code</h2><iframe id=\"iFrame1\" name=\"iFrame1\" width=\"100%\" onload=\"this.height=iFrame1.document.body.scrollHeight\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"/htmlcode/cf/cf1027c.html\" scrolling=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"yes\"></iframe>\n\n<h1 id=\"D\"><a href=\"#D\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"D\"></a>D</h1>","next":{"title":"cf#504(1023)","slug":"2018-08-18-cf_504_1023"},"link":"/2018/08/19","toc":[{"title":"A 签到题","id":"A-签到题","index":"1"},{"title":"B 填数+规律","id":"B-填数-规律","index":"2","children":[{"title":"题意","id":"题意","index":"2.1"},{"title":"做法一：分类讨论","id":"做法一：分类讨论","index":"2.2"},{"title":"做法二：规律","id":"做法二：规律","index":"2.3"},{"title":"code","id":"code","index":"2.4"}]},{"title":"C 签到题","id":"C-签到题","index":"3","children":[{"title":"code","id":"code-1","index":"3.1"}]},{"title":"D","id":"D","index":"4"}]}